                   (IoU) scores during training. More importantly, we also avoid
                   all hyper-parameters related to anchor boxes, which are often
                   sensitive to the final detection performance. With the only
                   post-processing non-maximum suppression (NMS), we demonstrate
                   a much simpler and flexible detection framework achieving
                   improved detection accuracy. We hope that the proposed FCOS
                   framework can serve as a simple and strong alternative for
                   many other instance-level tasks. Code and pre-trained models
                   are available at: https://git.io/AdelaiDet",
